webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Brokinds castle facility is located beautifully on a narrow land bridge between the lakes Järlunden and Lilla Rengen. The main building was built around 1730 after an older castle building was demolished in 1726 - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMFB000563. AB Flygtrafik. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021016419879. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
